room_title: Escape room "Apollo 920: Space Mission" by Locked Inside Room Escape in Melbourne
review: Such a great time! We did the space mission it was fun and tricky! Staff was super friendly and helpful. We will be back!

room_title: Escape room "Apollo 920: Space Mission" by Locked Inside Room Escape in Melbourne
review: Kaci, Olivia, and the team deliver as always in their new escape room Apollo 920. Very detail oriented and fun to play. Thanks so much for the fun and we will be back once you guys get the other new rooms ready!
